<plot>On the eve of her 80th birthday Hope Goodman reflects upon a life well lived. It is bitter sweet as she is flooded with memories, contemplating alone. The morning of her birthday brings messages from loved ones. Her excitement increases as she prepares in her dressing room for an evening at her favorite restaurant. While waiting, Hope realizes that she loves her life and is looking forward to the future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?117100</url></doc>
